data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom home in the highly sought after Westcliff neighborhood. Conveniently located on a quiet cul-de-sac, surrounded by mature landscaping. The heart of the home, the kitchen is a chef's delight, offering generous counter space, modern appliances, and beautiful windows that frame a scenic view of the backyard. A stunning back patio adorned with an oversized pergola. This space is perfect for family gatherings or entertaining guests, providing a seamless transition between indoor and outdoor living. This is more than a home; it's a haven for family living. Schedule a private tour to experience the charm and warmth of this exceptional property.
